Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.87,0:00:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.14,0:00:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.41,0:00:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.05,0:00:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繞過危險的轉角 追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.55,0:00:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.42,0:00:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.10,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.21,0:00:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.78,0:01:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.19,0:01:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.79,0:01:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.39,0:01:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.66,0:01:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.26,0:01:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.90,0:01:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.63,0:01:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞成這副模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.79,0:01:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.13,0:01:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無話可說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.83,0:01:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用實戰培養新人的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.57,0:01:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.11,0:01:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把記憶換到電子腦裡面行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,矢野不會再生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像GHOST無法複製
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.11,0:02:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算複製記憶 GHOST還是不會寄宿其中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果只考慮維持9課的運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.79,0:02:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們或許不需要新的人才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是考慮今後的情勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.86,0:02:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們不得不克服的課題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.70,0:02:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這次作戰還是不要安排阿東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請好好照顧他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.49,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#20 北端的混迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.20,0:02:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的老朋友給的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.37,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經確認前俄軍軍官 現在改行做黑手黨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波利斯•賈布羅夫和他的數名部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.64,0:03:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從該國運送鈽元素進入擇捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是說久世那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算去買那批鈽元素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.46,0:03:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想用核武器武裝自己 宣佈成為獨立國家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再大膽也要有個限度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臥底偵查的諜報員被他的改造人同伴殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以致他們現在行蹤不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諜報員被殺是2小時前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.58,0:03:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖然這麼說 我們其實已經沒有選擇餘地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們怎麼特定地點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡亂跑去擇捉也不會有結果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.93,0:04:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公安部給的情報裡面似乎有提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說擇捉市的佐川電子公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.34,0:04:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未經許可就擴建Berutarube區的地下工廠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Berutarube？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.64,0:04:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有俄國潛水艇基地的那個地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.08,0:04:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得俄軍撤退的時候 已經炸毀埋起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐川的擴建工程如果順利的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該已經挖到那個基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 真的很可疑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.86,0:04:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潛水艇基地的話 拿來藏偽裝船最合適
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有確切證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.97,0:04:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假設他們有在計劃那麼大的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當地的情報販子應該也會掌握到什麼才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.01,0:04:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,課長 我們就這樣進入擇捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.78,0:04:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一 請要求海上保安廳封鎖出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果難民拿到核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 所有的枷鎖都會解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.49,0:04:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我相信你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候如果不能抓到久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內廳的行為就會消失在黑暗當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍方也將介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓出島成為戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.07,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.51,0:05:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒有任何陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離交易還有一些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們輪班休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了\N知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要不要吃點這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.81,0:05:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道真的很糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得跟課長抗議才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要檢查一下電子腦活性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.62,0:06:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.56,0:06:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是對久世妄想的規模感到有點迷惑罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.73,0:06:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底有什麼樣的妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直截了當說的話 可以算是征服世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.24,0:06:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是無藥可救的誇大妄想狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.34,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你竟然會被那種東西迷惑\N一點都不像你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.64,0:06:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像思春期的小鬼\N遇到命中注定對象的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這樣一切就清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.49,0:06:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然個別的11人病毒在他身上發作過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.46,0:06:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他原本擁有的資質和思想產生了目前的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妄想本身確實很老套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們不能一笑置之的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.64,0:06:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是真心想要當上獨裁者來促成世界和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.44,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且腎上腺素的分泌已經達到正常人會死亡的量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該認定久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經進入聖域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖域是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是已經變成傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.43,0:07:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從歷史上來看 這種人可以發揮難以置信的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如「切•格瓦拉（古巴革命）」\N「麥康姆•X（黑人人權運動者）」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「卡西爾斯•克雷（拳王阿里）」就是這一類人的典型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟希特勒不同嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然某種意義上是同類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 思想上比較接近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是「甘地」和「金恩博士」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常常跟他連線的難民們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.88,0:07:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借由裝有劃分和過濾裝置的網絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉在他現場轉播的行為當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他之所以不加上偏見也不打算共享意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為他知道過了他的GHOST界線就是危險區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我那時也很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種話一點都不有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.93,0:08:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石川、帕茲、波瑪待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備交易地點錯誤時的支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 軍國主義者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經返還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.31,0:09:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 俄國人和日本人的摩擦不會馬上就消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建設中的地下空洞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能穿過這裡到達基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許就能跟久世見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們有那個運氣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.31,0:09:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候只能跟佐川的工程人員直接面對面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒多餘時間等少校的聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.89,0:10:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說要買武器 所以上了這艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.16,0:10:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 如果知道是你指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你不必勉強在這裡陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以就這樣回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者消失在擇捉的街頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會強迫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊成革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.65,0:10:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是最早教我們何謂革命的是「傳說」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.82,0:10:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在出島大部分的人都知道「久世同志」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.85,0:10:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是幾乎沒有人知道你的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不服氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.93,0:10:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在還是遵照「傳說」的指導\N有自爆的覺悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種做法只是自我滿足而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.27,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,革命是要有GHOST才會產生的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.61,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想知道你的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也給我能夠相信你的根據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.82,0:11:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.76,0:11:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.94,0:11:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們要拿到手的武器是鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.24,0:11:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用那個逼日本政府承認出島是獨立國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.05,0:11:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欠的東西要確實還清\N這是最低限度的規則不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺威風的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.13,0:11:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼可以借給別人的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.73,0:11:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是大姐頭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.66,0:11:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說克氯丹還在這裡面做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是真的 請這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是非常謹慎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.62,0:12:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣 請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德古沙 你在這裡等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.76,0:12:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也到這裡就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.39,0:12:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界太慇勤會惹人厭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.44,0:12:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.27,0:12:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟大姐頭一起工作很辛苦對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.01,0:12:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不跟大姐頭打好關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會後悔莫及的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克氯丹 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根室登陸作戰的時候 承蒙你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻性防壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛才被燒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.38,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潛入哪裡被燒死的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 能燒死克氯丹這種程度的黑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,技術相當高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.64,0:13:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻性防壁的運作方式也是機密保持法所不允許的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.22,0:13:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磁碟片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用這麼舊的東西當外部記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那傢伙花了那麼多功夫 就為了刪除這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐川的秘密帳簿嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出貨 檸檬蛋糕20公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檸檬蛋糕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每公斤50萬美金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M退出Au的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.02,0:14:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲介商 佐川K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B.J.\N檸檬蛋糕20公斤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.76,0:14:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K抽成40％＝退休金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買家\NB.P.介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所猜測的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他正在竊取鈽的交易情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐川的K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K是北端特務課長加賀崎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.41,0:14:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他擔任仲介買賣每公斤50萬美金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賣家是波利斯•賈布羅夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買家是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ASIAN／B．P.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是指亞洲難民…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說…剛剛的黑客是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.59,0:15:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加賀崎抽成的部分已經改成日元了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.66,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經把頭款匯給佐川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2億4千萬日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.04,0:15:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難民從哪裡拿到這麼一大筆錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久世準備的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.34,0:15:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的話 他是怎麼辦到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 幫了我大忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.18,0:15:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得你說過佐川電子\N是你最討厭的日系企業啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該辭掉報道廳的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.13,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 內廳說不定會是個比較好一點的機構
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.10,0:15:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石川 交易地點在核潛艇基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個案子也有可能跟內廳有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.24,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.08,0:15:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴特他們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經在地底深處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.71,0:15:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通訊受到阻隔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上過去那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.83,0:16:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再告訴我一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說買鈽至少要25萬美金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這筆錢你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從俄國人手上騙過來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.24,0:16:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我會老實付錢買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓國民理解我們的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢是我請一直消費難民的國民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點一點「捐」出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣說你大概聽不懂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個設計是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.53,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在那些對自己的豐衣足食\N毫無自覺的國民總儲蓄額
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很輕鬆就超過900兆日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.03,0:16:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實他們對這個數字也毫無自覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後你知道這些儲蓄的利息當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一筆表面上不存在的金額嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表面上不存在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是一日元以下的金額
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終端機資料上通常也沒有顯示的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小數點以下的數字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要從網絡上的帳戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徵收這微薄幾分錢的金額
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.16,0:17:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天就有數千萬計的金額
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.43,0:17:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我設計程序把這些錢匯進我的銀行戶頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢就是從那裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人根本不知道自己的帳戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.18,0:17:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有小數點以下的存款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.62,0:17:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀行現在都把帳戶管理交給AI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.35,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難民在這個國家工作明明就要預先扣稅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻完全不允許歸化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國民還是我行我素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.33,0:17:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒注意到系統做了多嚴重的壓搾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.30,0:17:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只攝取著順口又容易接受的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是一個欺瞞的社會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓大家知道這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.74,0:18:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那筆錢現在到底有多少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,107億6千萬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的革命所能用的軍事資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一個恐怖分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.43,0:18:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在有點醉心於英雄主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.41,0:18:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓船準備好隨時可以出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是有問題的擴建區域嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.73,0:18:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該有得到許可吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是現場的負貴人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你剛剛說「又來了」對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久前來了2台母公司的武裝機甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.74,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再之前是一個俄國的奇怪改造人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.38,0:19:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提著兩個大皮箱下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.18,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中獎了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.95,0:19:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.98,0:19:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼陸上自衛隊也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有你一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.71,0:19:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賈布羅夫與加賀崎都被公安盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一個人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點完成交易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.83,0:20:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.73,0:20:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是指定帳戶的匯款記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去確認吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.95,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們等一下馬上過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交易成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.53,0:20:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此都一樣無法確認內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丟下武器出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.54,0:21:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以違反兵器管製法和非法交易核物質的罪名逮捕你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我看你的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.78,0:22:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,齋籐 有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.81,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要管這裡 快去抓柯伊爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.42,0:22:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.19,0:22:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.12,0:22:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要確實破壞掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.03,0:22:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住 久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那個放到地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不立刻開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你知道這是什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.42,0:22:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.28,0:22:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的獵物是你的人頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.82,0:22:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那恐怕很困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.99,0:22:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點把皮箱拿到船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.26,0:22:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…\N快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.93,0:22:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧不起我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.45,0:23:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.15,0:23:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.73,0:23:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣美麗的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.03,0:23:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.57,0:23:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.64,0:23:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.18,0:23:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我省視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.45,0:23:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.55,0:23:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.92,0:23:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.93,0:24:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在軀殼裡的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.06,0:24:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.90,0:24:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我省視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.91,0:24:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.15,0:24:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.65,0:24:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.55,0:24:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這個軀殼裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.66,0:24:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻殼車式的日常生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.20,0:24:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都已經到達光站著都不可思議的程度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.10,0:24:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的能看到對手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.01,0:24:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 攻殼車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.48,0:24:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用鋼絲跳到武裝機甲上面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.68,0:24:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會出現嗎 最強的招數「立式迴旋碎擊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.05,0:24:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來武裝機甲已經沒有勝算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.02,0:24:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.15,0:24:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經精疲力盡了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.92,0:25:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.13,0:25:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來明明是雙方該表現的時候\N卻很沒用地同時倒下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.26,0:25:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都站不起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.43,0:25:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣很沒用\N可是差不多該到說再見的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.80,0:25:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個電腦空間繼續沉浸在一種異樣的沒用氣氛中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.04,0:25:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現場由我攻殼車負責轉播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.84,0:25:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒用到非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.98,0:25:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就很沒用地說再見…
